https://conda.io/projects/conda/en/latest/user-guide/tasks/manage-environments.html#creating-an-environment-with-commands

Basic to create one:
1. conda create --name myenv
2. proceed ([y]/n)?

venv with specific py ver:
1. conda create -n myenv python=3.9

venv with specific package:
1. conda create -n myenv scipy

venv with specific version of package:
1. conda create -n myenv scipy=0.17.3

venv with specific version of Python and multiple packages:
1. conda create -n myenv python=3.9 scipy=0.17.3 astroid babel
